parted /dev/xvdf
# (parted) help                 - to see a list of commands
# (parted) print                - to take a look at the partition table
# (parted) resizepart           - to resize a partition
# Partition number? 1           - we choose partition 1
# End?  [10.0GB] 15000          - size = 15GB (the default untis are in MB)
# (parted) quit                 - quit